sourcesContent: import * as React from 'react'; import { PFColors } from '../components/Pf/PfColors'; import { AngleDoubleDownIcon, AngleDoubleLeftIcon, AngleDoubleRightIcon, AngleDoubleUpIcon, AngleDownIcon, AngleLeftIcon, AngleRightIcon, ApplicationsIcon, ArrowLeftIcon, AsteriskIcon, BanIcon, BellIcon, BlueprintIcon, BoltIcon, BundleIcon, CloseIcon, CodeBranchIcon, CompressIcon, CopyIcon, EllipsisHIcon, ErrorCircleOIcon, ExpandIcon, GlobeAmericasIcon, GlobeRouteIcon, HelpIcon, HistoryIcon, HomeIcon, InfoAltIcon, InProgressIcon, LockIcon, LockOpenIcon, OkIcon, OnRunningIcon, OutlinedClockIcon, PauseCircleIcon, PauseIcon, PficonTemplateIcon, PlayCircleIcon, PlayIcon, RepositoryIcon, ServiceIcon, ShareAltIcon, StopIcon, TopologyIcon, UnknownIcon, UserClockIcon, WarningTriangleIcon, ProcessAutomationIcon } from '@patternfly/react-icons'; import { style } from 'typestyle'; export const defaultIconStyle = style({ // nothing special }); const iconStyle = style({ width: '10px' }); interface IconProps { className?: string; color?: string; } // keep alphabetized export const KialiIcon: { [name: string]: React.FunctionComponent } = { AngleDoubleDown: (props: IconProps) => , AngleDoubleLeft: (props: IconProps) => , AngleDoubleRight: (props: IconProps) => , AngleDoubleUp: (props: IconProps) => , AngleDown: (props: IconProps) => , AngleLeft: (props: IconProps) => , AngleRight: (props: IconProps) => , Applications: (props: IconProps) => , Back: (props: IconProps) => , Bell: (props: IconProps) => , CircuitBreaker: (props: IconProps) => , Clock: (props: IconProps) => , Close: (props: IconProps) => , Compress: (props: IconProps) => , Copy: (props: IconProps) => , Error: (props: IconProps) => , Expand: (props: IconProps) => , FaultInjection: (props: IconProps) => , Gateway: (props: IconProps) => , Help: (props: IconProps) => , History: (props: IconProps) => , Info: (props: IconProps) => , IstioConfig: (props: IconProps) => , InProgressIcon: (props: IconProps) => , LocalTime: (props: IconProps) => , MissingSidecar: (props: IconProps) => , MoreLegend: (props: IconProps) => , MtlsLock: (props: IconProps) => , MtlsUnlock: (props: IconProps) => , Ok: (props: IconProps) => , OnRunningIcon: (props: IconProps) => , Pause: (props: IconProps) => , PauseCircle: (props: IconProps) => , Play: (props: IconProps) => , PlayCircle: (props: IconProps) => , Regex: (props: IconProps) => , Repository: (props: IconProps) => , RequestRouting: (props: IconProps) => , ResetSettings: (props: IconProps) => , RequestTimeout: (props: IconProps) => , Services: (props: IconProps) => , Stop: (props: IconProps) => , Topology: (props: IconProps) => , TrafficShifting: (props: IconProps) => , Unknown: (props: IconProps) => , UserClock: (props: IconProps) => , VirtualService: (props: IconProps) => , Warning: (props: IconProps) => ( ), Website: (props: IconProps) => , Workloads: (props: IconProps) => }; Object.keys(KialiIcon).forEach(key => { KialiIcon[key].defaultProps = { className: iconStyle }; }); // createTooltipIcon wraps the icon in a span element. Tooltip child elements that are // SVGs (icons) need to be wrapped in something to avoid the tooltip from disappearing on refresh. // See: https://github.com/kiali/kiali/issues/3583 for more details. export function createTooltipIcon(icon: any) { return {icon}; }
